.SH "STDIN AGENTS:BOOTSTRAP"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin agents:bootstrap [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-dry\-run\fR
Print actions without executing (mutates nothing)
.SH "STDIN AGENTS:CLEAN"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin agents:clean [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-name\fR
Clean one agent by name (or set NAME env var)
.TP
\fB\-\-all\fR
Clean every agent and sandbox/logs/ (or set ALL=1)
.SH "STDIN AGENTS:FLEET"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin agents:fleet [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-reset\fR
Pass \-\-reset to agents:ready (run db:reset first)
.TP
\fB\-\-seed\fR
Pass \-\-seed to agents:ready (run db:seed after reset)
.SH "STDIN AGENTS:HEADLESS"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin agents:headless [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-prompt\fR
Override the neutral nudge prompt (or set PROMPT env var)
.SH "STDIN AGENTS:READY"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin agents:ready [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-reset\fR
Run 'mise run db:reset' before polling
.TP
\fB\-\-seed\fR
Run 'mise run db:seed' after reset (non\-empty deck backdrop)
.TP
\fB\-\-timeout\fR
Seconds to wait for /health (default 60)
.SH "STDIN AGENTS:REPORT"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin agents:report [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-name\fR
Limit report to one agent by name (or set NAME env var)
.TP
\fB\-\-since\fR
Only show DB activity since ISO timestamp (or set SINCE env var)
.SH "STDIN AGENTS:SYNC"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin agents:sync [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-check\fR
Exit non\-zero if files are out of sync (CI drift check)
.SH "STDIN DEV:ENSURE-PORTS"
\fBUsage:\fR stdin dev:ensure\-ports [OPTIONS]
.PP
\fBOptions:\fR
.PP
.TP
\fB\-\-force\fR
Regenerate .dev/ports.env even if it already exists
